{"id":2835,"date":"2022-04-12T16:00:34","date_gmt":"2022-04-12T10:30:34","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/?p=2835"},"modified":"2022-07-08T12:49:02","modified_gmt":"2022-07-08T07:19:02","slug":"top-mobile-application-development-trends-2020","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/top-mobile-application-development-trends-2020.html","title":{"rendered":"Top Mobile App Development Trends 2022"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-9986\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/mobile-application-development-trends-2022.jpg\" alt=\"Mobile Application Development Trends in 2022\" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/mobile-application-development-trends-2022.jpg 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/mobile-application-development-trends-2022-300x146.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/mobile-application-development-trends-2022-768x373.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>It\u2019s been 14 eventful years since the mobile revolution took flight in 2008, and for all associated with the vast world of mobile apps, there is no looking back. Not only does it bring myriad opportunities for connoisseurs of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/mobile-app-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">mobile application development<\/a>, the end users of mobile application are the biggest benefactor considering the value it has added to everyday life, education, entertainment quotient and improving business productivity. Presenting a consolidated report on the thriving Mobile app development trends&nbsp;in 2022.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_Makes_Mobile_App_Development_the_Most_Lucrative_Business_Opportunity\"><\/span>What Makes Mobile App Development the Most Lucrative Business Opportunity?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>In 2018, global mobile app revenues amounted to over 365 billion U.S. dollars. In 2023, mobile apps are projected to generate more than 935 billion U.S. dollars in revenues via paid downloads and in-app advertising. Mobile app consumer expenditure in the Americas amounted to 17.5 billion U.S. dollars. In 2022, consumers in this region are projected to spend over 34 billion U.S. dollars on mobile apps via app stores.<\/p>\n<p>But, what\u2019s driving the Mobile app development demand? Well, studies have been consistently pointing at engagement-driven in-app purchases and an integrated cross-device experience fueling this demand. The new iOS 9 update although with small changes is stated to make a big impact in mobile app development in 2022. Similarly, Android developers are also benefiting from the latest Google update in building apps that thrive competition and show on top of the charts.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mobility_%E2%80%93_Redefining_the_Future_of_Enterprise_Application_Development\"><\/span>Mobility &#8211; Redefining the Future of Enterprise Application Development<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Industry experts are betting on mobile devices and applications to continue bringing in a plethora of opportunities for commercial and technical innovation in 2022. This will include creating new ways to improve process efficiency and effectiveness inside the organization, besides delivering innovative products, services and customer relationships outside it.<\/p>\n<p>However, mobility requires mastering a wide range of technologies and capabilities so as to unlock its full potential. Here are the <strong>top 5 must-have technologies, businesses should include as part of their Mobile App Development Strategies for 2022<\/strong>:<\/p>\n<p><center><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2842\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/mobile-app-trends-collage.jpg\" alt=\"mobile-app-trends-collage\" width=\"600\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/mobile-app-trends-collage.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/12\/mobile-app-trends-collage-300x150.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/center><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Multiplatform_Multi-architecture_AD_Tools\"><\/span>Multiplatform\/ Multi-architecture AD Tools<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>With many multiplatform development tools available, it is now indispensable for businesses to procure application development (AD) tools to support a &#8220;3 x 3&#8221; future that is an assimilation of 3 key platforms (Android, iOS and Windows) and 3 app architectures (native, hybrid and mobile Web using HTML5). This is important considering its complex balancing act in trading off many technical and nontechnical issues.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"HTML5\"><\/span>HTML5<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>One of the <strong>most powerful tools that can play a key role in mobile app development in 2022<\/strong>, considering its ability to deliver apps across multiple platforms, especially for employee-facing situations when the highest quality of user experience isn\u2019t essential. Besides being supported in most versions of smartphones and tablets, HTML5 when it comes to coding, complements but does not replace native code. So users should be ready to experience disappointing on poor-performance smartphones and slow network connections.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Advanced_Mobile_UX_Design\"><\/span>Advanced Mobile UX Design<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Mobile UX design is going to play an exceptional role in mobile app development in 2022, as app developers by now have realized the flipside of poor user experience \u2013 one of the most common contributors to low app-store ratings. High-quality mobile app UXs is indispensable considering it directly impacts ROI or customer satisfaction.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"High-Precision_Location_Sensing\"><\/span>High-Precision Location Sensing<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Identifying an individual\u2019s location in a precise area can be a key enabler for the delivery of highly relevant contextual information and services. You can find apps harnessing precise indoor location currently use technologies such as Wi-Fi, imaging, ultrasonic beacons and geomagnetism. This is crucial considering an increase in use of beacons (based on the low-energy Bluetooth Smart standard) in 2022.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Wearables\"><\/span>Wearables<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Wearables or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/wearable-device-application-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">wearable apps<\/a> are to be the most watched out for in 2022 as they fuel your healthcare sensors, smart jewelry, smart watches, display devices. The wearables industry is expected to grow into a multibillion-dollar market, and trends reflect at a sizable domination by sports and fitness sensors.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Latest_Mobile_App_Development_Trends_in_2022\"><\/span>Latest Mobile App Development Trends in 2022<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Machine_learning_and_AI\"><\/span>Machine learning and AI<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Machine learning has already started to replace mobile apps and is considered to be one of the most sought-after mobile app development trends in 2022. Artificial intelligence and machine learning is being used for chatbots, face unlock systems and in voice searching. Artificial intelligence is being used in various photo applications for the development of photo filters.<\/p>\n<p>Mobile companies are using artificial intelligence for face detection, image recognition, classification of images and texts, recognition of speech, recognition of sentiment and predictive analysis. Machine learning and artificial intelligence would enable mobile applications to become smarter and improve their overall efficiency.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Augmented_Reality_in_mobile_apps\"><\/span>Augmented Reality in mobile apps<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>The use of augmented reality in mobile apps is on a steep rise in 2022. Augmented reality has found its utilization in several aspects of mobile phones such as gaming, videos and cameras. In 2022, virtual reality and augmented reality has been seen to come up with features like people occlusion and tracking motion of individuals. Augmented reality will not only be responsible for changing the mobile phone industry but would also benefit industries like e-commerce, tourism, healthcare and education.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Beacon_Technology\"><\/span>Beacon Technology<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/much-know-beacon-technology.html\">Beacon technology<\/a> has found its utility in a wide range of industries around the world. Beacon Technology has become a rage in 2022 because it helps to provide added functionality to almost every mobile application. The application when present on mobile phone displays stores that are selling the required product along with the specifications and its prices when did inter Abby come zone. The added advantage of the technology is that it helps business owners to track consumer behavior within their stores.<\/p>\n<p>In today\u2019s data driven world, this technology would find wide uses in the marketing industry. It has the potential to reduce bridges between companies and their consumers. This technology would help a business owner of a retail store to determine the amount of time a customer is spending on a particular oil. The application would provide automatic notification to the customers to inform them about sales related to those products on later dates.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Blockchain_Technology\"><\/span>Blockchain Technology<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Block chain technology is considered as a leading player among other latest mobile app development trends. While the Blockchain technology might remind you of cryptocurrencies, the use of blockchain technology has evolved in various other areas. With the significant increase in the use of mobile wallets Blockchain technology has found its utilization in the same. It is used to keep a track of digital assets, loyalty programmes and help to secure an individual\u2018s digital identity. Is also used to develop solutions for cloud storage.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On-demand_applications\"><\/span>On-demand applications<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>On demand application is among other mobile app development trends that are reaching new heights in 2022. On demand applications are filling the gaps that are existing in the mobile application development industry. Generally development of applications requires a certain level of knowledge and technical expertise on coding. Is very difficult for small-scale businesses to look for apps that could be used to scale their businesses. On-demand applications are remediating these problems. On-demand applications have made the app development process significantly accessible.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"App_Security_to_be_in_focus\"><\/span>App Security to be in focus<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>With over 75 percent of mobile apps facing basic security measures through 2019, it is also likely to be the prime focus in 2020. Even though platforms like Apple\u2019s iOS 13 or Android 10.0 are already known for its high-end security features, developers have to ensure that the secure running of the apps, without negotiating the integrity of the platform.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cloud-based_Apps_to_be_the_flavor_of_the_year\"><\/span>Cloud-based Apps to be the flavor of the year<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>After playing a comprehensive role in mobile app development in 2029, cloud technology is all set to continue spreading its magic in 2020. One of the reasons for the success of cloud-based apps is that developers can keep the actual size of their mobile apps small; and secondly, cloud compatibility allows users to sync their apps across multiple devices.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Enterprise_App_will_Receive_More_Traction\"><\/span>Enterprise App will Receive More Traction<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Studies predict enterprise apps to show more traction in 2020 over consumer apps, with almost 20 percent of global developers targeting this segment considering better ROI. It is also estimated that 35 percent of all large enterprises will have their own mobile app development platforms.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mobile_Banking_and_M-commerce\"><\/span>Mobile Banking and M-commerce<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>79% of smartphone users have made a purchase online using their mobile device in the last 6 months.&nbsp; Moreover, with the use of mobile phones to become as smart as using cards while shopping; analysts predict this trend to continue in the upcoming years &#8211; irrespective of whether it involves transferring money or shopping online. This means developers will focus more on developing mobile apps that can do transactions simply using credit cards.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Internet_of_Things_IoT_is_here\"><\/span>The Internet of Things (IoT) is here!<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>With the IoT market expected to grow 31.72 percent (CAGR) between 2014 and 2019, the Internet of things is predicted to emerge more than just a buzzword in 2020. Thanks to the rising awareness of a \u2018connected\u2019 world, it is all set to take app development to the next stage. And the possibilities are even brighter with the World Economic Forum predicting \u201cover 5 billion people will be connected to each other, across 50 billion things\u201d.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Impact_of_5G_Wireless\"><\/span>Impact of 5G Wireless<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Undoubtedly, 5G technology is going to be one of the top trends in mobile app development and will be of great significance in 2020 and beyond. One of the first things which comes to mind when we talk about the 5G network is speed; stated to be approximately 100 times faster than the 4G network.<\/p>\n<p>There definitely is time for 5G to get in the groove this year but by year-end, we can expect to see a shift from currently used 4G services to the 5G wireless network. However, industry experts have been betting high on the 5G technology already.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ricardian_Contracts\"><\/span>Ricardian Contracts<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>This may sound new to some. Defining a Ricardian contract, it is a legal agreement which is agreed and signed upon by both of the parties involved in the contract. One can convert it into a machine-readable contract that also defines the intentions of the involved parties. This is especially good for blockchain development related to payment and financial transactions. One can easily <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/hire-mobile-app-developers.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hire mobile app developers<\/a> who can help in design &amp; development of such DApps or decentralized apps for mobile.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Low-Code_Development\"><\/span>Low-Code Development<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Just as the name suggests, Low code development basically eliminates the tedious work for a large amount of manual coding, eventually reducing the complexity of development. With Low-code platforms, developers can scale the applications as and when the application size and business grows. Some of the currently popular Low-code development tools are OutSystems, Appian, Google App Builder, Kissflow, Zoho Creator, etc. and they are gaining more popularity by the day.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Android_Instant_Apps\"><\/span>Android Instant Apps<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Back in 2016 Google launched Instant apps in order to make things more convenient for developers and users alike. They are nothing but native apps which function like websites and can attract people with their functionalities.<\/p>\n<p>You can consider it as a trial for many apps that users can get access to without downloading them. Google Instant apps are available for the users in the Play Store where they can access the apps instantly sans the need to download. As of now, there are a limited number of Instant apps available in the Google Play Store. More apps are expected to go live in the coming months.<\/p>\n<p>Some of the major benefits of these instant apps are that they are smaller in size, possess functionalities of a website, provide excellent user experience and do not use device memory.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mobile_Wallets_on_the_Rise\"><\/span>Mobile Wallets on the Rise<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>With the rise in e-commerce and online banking, there has been a tremendous growth in the availability of online payments for customers. With the rise of Apple Pay and Google Wallet, customers have found themselves shifting gradually into m-commerce. On the other hand, Blockchain is entering into the mobile payments and powering the apps with more secured money transaction options for customers all over.<\/p>\n<p>Previously, cash got replaced by the plastic money, and now it&#8217;s time for the plastic money to vanish. Welcome online payments.<\/p>\n<p>Many tech giants like Samsung and Apple are working to build an enhanced scan and pay technique which will make money transactions and bill payments more convenient. They also want to enable the peer-to-peer money payment system with its own payment systems like Apple Pay.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Are_you_ready_to_take_on_the_world\"><\/span>Are you ready to take on the world?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Well, there is a lot of enthusiasm amongst mobile app developers regarding mobile <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/ios-app-development-trends-to-watch-out.html\">app development trends<\/a> in 2022 as innovative concepts, trending technologies and challenging platforms are opening up opportunities for creating enhanced applications.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/top-mobile-application-development-trends-2020.html\/#What_Makes_Mobile_App_Development_the_Most_Lucrative_Business_Opportunity\" title=\"What Makes Mobile App Development the Most Lucrative Business Opportunity?\">What Makes Mobile App Development the Most Lucrative Business Opportunity?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/top-mobile-application-development-trends-2020.html\/#Mobility_%E2%80%93_Redefining_the_Future_of_Enterprise_Application_Development\" title=\"Mobility &#8211; Redefining the Future of Enterprise Application Development\">Mobility &#8211; Redefining the Future of Enterprise Application Development<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/top-mobile-application-development-trends-2020.html\/#Multiplatform_Multi-architecture_AD_Tools\" title=\"Multiplatform\/ Multi-architecture AD Tools\">Multiplatform\/ Multi-archite